# =============================================================================
# Runtime state — regenerated on every run, never commit
# =============================================================================
# Y1.004+: state lives in <repo>/state/ which fs.link maps to a persistent
# drive outside the panel install. Pre-Y1.004 root-level paths are kept
# below so existing installs don't leak files into commits during the
# one-time migration window (state files get moved into state/ on first
# Y1.004 boot — see _migrate_state_dir in mlx_ltx_panel.py).
state
state/
panel_queue.json
panel_hidden.json
panel_settings.json
# 2026-05-31 review: defense-in-depth for the private GitHub-stats data.
# `state/` is an fs.link symlink off-repo, so `git check-ignore
# state/stats-data.jsonl` reports "beyond a symbolic link" — i.e. the only
# thing protecting it today is that it lives outside the repo. A basename
# rule covers it even if PHOSPHENE_STATS_OUT is pointed somewhere tracked,
# or the symlink is ever replaced with a real dir. (A snapshot leaked once
# to docs/stats-data.jsonl — rolled back in 70b4489. Never again.)
**/stats-data.jsonl
stats-data.jsonl
*.log
*.tmp
# Manual `.original_<date>` asset backups (e.g. before re-exporting a logo).
# Kept on disk for the author, never committed / shipped (v3.0.7 review P3).
*.original_*

# =============================================================================
# Generated / user content — too big or too personal for git
# =============================================================================
mlx_outputs
mlx_outputs/
panel_uploads
panel_uploads/
audio_inputs
audio_inputs/

# =============================================================================
# Models — ~60 GB, must be downloaded separately (see README)
# =============================================================================
mlx_models
mlx_models/

# =============================================================================
# Third-party — installed alongside, not part of this repo
# =============================================================================
ltx-2-mlx/
.venv/

# =============================================================================
# Legacy experimentation files (Comfy workflows, etc.) — not part of the panel
# =============================================================================
civitai_ltxv23_workflow/
ltx23_*.json
ltx_latest_test_view.html
run_ltx_mlx_i2v.sh

# =============================================================================
# Python
# =============================================================================
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.egg-info/

# =============================================================================
# Local environment / secrets — never commit
# =============================================================================
# .env.local holds Linear API key and any other per-machine secrets used by
# agent tooling (e.g. Linear project sync). Source-of-truth credential file
# is ~/claude/claudio/.env; .env.local just mirrors what this folder needs.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# =============================================================================
# OS / IDE
# =============================================================================
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Claude Preview tool config (per-machine, not Phosphene)
.claude/
